{"lastModified":1773831285174,"uri":"c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: France, Corsica, Sardinia, Italy, Marseille, Balearic Is., Spain, Caribbean Sea\n\nIKIGAI was recently refitted and refurbished at Vitters Shipyard in what was effectively a complete rebuild. The spacious, modern and welcoming interior is fashioned from clear varnished teak. The large master cabin and two guest cabins are situated forward. Amidships are the spacious saloon and dining room. Behind the companionway you will find, to port, the brand-new high-tech navigation station, the chart table and the crew cabin; and to starboard, the galley and crew mess. The transom opens to give access to the garage where the tender is stored. Sailing IKIGAI is an absolute joy: sensational to helm, she is simply fantastic upwind.","blueprint":{"name":"IKIGAI","images":["/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-4004-AfuGSGMuX.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::02a25cc0-53d1-11ef-b376-d978e088662a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::02a32010-53d1-11ef-b376-d978e088662a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::02a47fa0-53d1-11ef-b376-d978e088662a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::02a39540-53d1-11ef-b376-d978e088662a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::02a51be0-53d1-11ef-b376-d978e088662a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::02a65460-53d1-11ef-b376-d978e088662a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::02a5b820-53d1-11ef-b376-d978e088662a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::02a6a280-53d1-11ef-b376-d978e088662a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::02a6a280-53d1-11ef-b377-d978e088662a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::02a7b3f0-53d1-11ef-b377-d978e088662a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::02a6f0a0-53d1-11ef-b376-d978e088662a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::02a82920-53d1-11ef-9347-6d6cead916d0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::02a78ce0-53d1-11ef-b377-d978e088662a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::02a89e50-53d1-11ef-b377-d978e088662a/{imageVariant}"],"make":" JFA","model":"JFA/Vitters 82","maxCrew":2,"sleeps":8,"basePort":{"uri":"a::place::084d3462-b3ee-11ed-96e3-325096b39f47","name":"Palma","coordinates":{"latitude":39.56851771,"longitude":2.644393321},"country":"Spain"},"builtYear":2002,"architect":"Judel / Vrolijk & Co","interiorDesigner":"","refitYear":2024,"topSpeed":"","cruiseSpeed":12,"fuelCapacity":1400,"cabinLayout":[{"label":"Master Cabin","value":"1"},{"label":"Twin Cabins","value":"2"}],"cabins":3,"length":25.13,"beam":6,"draft":3.5,"hullType":"","hullConstruction":"Aluminium","tonnage":"","superStructure":[],"engines":"1 x 300HP Yanmar","amenities":[{"label":"Generators"}],"toys":[{"label":"Kite Surf","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Scuba Diving Equipment"},{"label":"Snorkeling equipment"},{"label":"Golf clubs"},{"label":"Seabob"},{"label":"Fishing equipment"},{"label":"Hammocks"}],"entertainment":[],"tenders":["1 x 13'9 / 4.2m RIB with 40 HP engine"]},"crew":[{"name":"Andreas Buhl","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::ac1bbd50-f07e-11f0-8c47-b136061ebfc8/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Sail and Work Experience\nAndreas grew up in a sailing family and has been involved in sailing and boat maintenance since childhood. With over 20 years of licensed experience in the yachting industry, he has served as captain and skipper across Europe and internationally. His background includes hands-on involvement in yacht refits, equipping him with a solid understanding of engineering and maintenance. Andreas enjoys all sorts of water sports, as well as fishing and the preparation of fine sea food. More recently, he has formed a professional Captain/Hostess team with his wife Katrin, delivering seamless and memorable charter experiences.\n\nJob Description\nAs Captain, the overall running of the vessel is Andreas’ responsibility; this includes the navigation, safety, and experience of all onboard. He ensures that IKIGAI runs smoothly and efficiently whilst adhering to all the appropriate regulations.\n\nLicenses and Qualifications\n• RYA/MCA Yachtmaster Offshore Commercial Endorsement\n• RYA/MCA Yachtmaster Ocean Commercial Endorsement\n• RYA/MCA Short Range Certificate\n• STCW95 Personal Safety & Social Responsibility, Personal Survival Techniques, Fire Prevention and Firefighting, Elementary First Aid\n• Yachtmaster Licence (sail & power) for Navigation Areas 1 & 2 – Austrian Yachting Association (ÖSV)\n• PADI Open Water Certificate\n\nLanguages:\nGerman, English, Spanish, Dutch\n"},{"name":"Katrin Groch","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::7579668770::vessel::d5cb5c97-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c3d42090-f07e-11f0-9e88-4fa565883ad6/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Sail and Work Experience\nKatrin has been sailing with the captain for the past four years and has completed two ocean crossings, demonstrating her reliability and capability at sea. With a professional background as a Personal Assistant, she brings strong experience in VIP communication and support. Onboard, she enjoys stewardess duties and cooking, contributing to a warm and professional atmosphere while enhancing the overall guest experience.\n\nJob Description\nKatrin is responsible for interior duties including guest hospitality, meal service, and maintaining cleanliness and comfort throughout the yacht. Her background in VIP support ensures attentive and discreet service, while her enjoyment of cooking adds a personal touch to onboard life. \n\nLanguages\nGerman, English\n"}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":2800000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2800000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":3200000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":3200000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Summer: Low Season","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-05-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-06-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-10-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":2800000,"inputAmountTaxed":"NONE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":2800000,"amount":2800000}],"total":2800000,"subTotal":2800000,"totalTax":0},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"France","type":"Country","category":["Europe","Western Europe","France"],"coordinates":[-3.676762491181631,13.257370810531999],"bbox":[-61.79784094999991,-21.37078215899993,55.854502800000034,51.08754088371883]},{"label":"Corsica","type":"Geo subunit","category":["Europe","Southern Europe","Corsica"],"coordinates":[9.104917129771797,42.161865413836736],"bbox":[8.565625000000011,41.384912109374994,9.556445312500017,43.021484375]},{"label":"Sardinia","type":"Geo subunit","category":["Europe","Southern Europe","Sardinia"],"coordinates":[8.96574354539669,40.12242872762209],"bbox":[8.180859375000011,38.90966796875,9.805273437500006,41.257080078125]},{"label":"Italy","type":"Sovereign cou